This article is a statement by the President of the United States on the anniversary of the assassination of former Lebanese Prime Minister Rafiq Hariri. The President expresses grief over the loss of Prime Minister Hariri and emphasizes that his sacrifice will not be in vain. The United States fully supports the Special Tribunal for Lebanon, which will begin its work soon, to bring those responsible for the assassination and subsequent crimes to justice. The United States also pledges support for Lebanon's sovereignty, independence, and legitimate institutions, as well as the implementation of UN Security Council Resolutions 1701 and 1559. The President encourages peace, moderation, national reconciliation, and prosperity for the Lebanese people.